Instrument Cluster – Speedster/VX220

Changes to the instrument cluster are as follows:

  • New silver background
  • Warning lamp symbols aligned to current ISO 7000 standard
  • New lettering
  • New fuel gauge, consisting of a horizontal bar of LCD segments
  • Anti-theft alarm warning lamp, relocated from the centre console to the tachometer
